episodes.title: Are you in cult?
episodes.description: Tonight for part 2 of our look into cults, we discuss the psychology of both members and leaders. Personality traits & behavior's to look out for. We discuss the 3 types of cults and their differences.

episodes.title: CULTS - Are you in one?
episodes.description:
Cults have been a part of humanity since we started writing things down, probably even before then.
Join us as we go through what is a CULT, how cults form, their egomaniacal and greed driven leaders, and we will do a quick look at a few of our favourite stories about cults.
